---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="How to Order Chemicals Online" description="Order industrial chemicals from UE Chemicals. Simple process for Caluanie, Red Mercury & Silver Mercury. Worldwide shipping from Bangkok, Thailand. Request a quote." activePage="ordering">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">How to Order</div>
      <h1>Ordering Information for Industrial Chemicals</h1>
      <p>Follow our simple ordering process to get the chemicals you need, delivered safely and on time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ordering Steps -->
  <section class="steps-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="section-label">Step by Step</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">How to Place Your Order</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h4>Contact Our Sales Team</h4>
          <p>Reach out to our dedicated sales team via WhatsApp or email to discuss your specific requirements. Our experts will provide detailed product information, pricing, and availability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h4>Request a Quote</h4>
          <p>Submit a request for a quote by filling out our online order form or contacting our sales team. Be sure to include all relevant details such as product type, quantity, and shipping preferences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h4>Confirm Your Order</h4>
          <p>Once you receive a comprehensive quote, confirm your order by responding to the quote or providing a purchase order (PO). Our team will process your order and provide an estimated delivery timeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h4>Payment Options</h4>
          <p>We offer flexible payment methods, including bank transfers, credit card payments, and other secure options. Payment terms will be discussed during the ordering process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h4>Order Tracking and Updates</h4>
          <p>After placing your order, you will receive tracking information and updates on the status of your shipment to ensure full transparency and peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Shipping Info -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="two-col-text">
          <div class="section-label">Delivery</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Reliable and Timely Shipping</h2>
          <p>We understand the importance of timely delivery for your operations. UE Chemicals partners with reputable shipping companies to guarantee safe and prompt delivery of all orders, both domestically and internationally.</p>
          
          <h5 style="margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:0.9rem;">Shipping Methods</h5>
          <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:20px;">
            <li style="color:var(--body-text);margin-bottom:8px;">Standard Ground Shipping (Europe / ADR)</li>
            <li style="color:var(--body-text);margin-bottom:8px;">Expedited Shipping Options</li>
            <li style="color:var(--body-text);margin-bottom:8px;">International Freight Services</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top:15px;"><strong style="color:var(--black);">Estimated Delivery Times:</strong> Delivery times may vary based on location and product availability. Estimated timelines will be provided when your order is confirmed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col-image">
          <img src="/images/Applications-of-Our-Industrial-Chemicals.jpg" alt="Shipping & Delivery" style="height:400px;object-fit:cover;width:100%;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Safety & Compliance -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h5>Shipping Safety</h5>
          <p>All products are packaged according to industry safety standards to prevent any damage or contamination during transit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h5>Safety and Compliance</h5>
          <p>We ensure that all our products meet stringent safety and compliance standards for storage, transportation, and usage. Safety Data Sheets (SDS) are provided with your order.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h5>Need Assistance?</h5>
          <p>Our dedicated team is here to help you every step of the way. For questions, assistance with your order, or further information, please <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--accent);">contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Place Your Order?</h2>
      <p>Contact our sales team today to get started with your chemical order.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent">Contact Us <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
